  "texts": [
    "• In this investigation, we propose a ViT-based architecture for pneumonia detection in CXR.",
    "This architecture will be designed to effectively manage the large and complex medical images that are typical in CXR and will be capable of detecting pneumonia with precision.",
    "• We will evaluate the accuracy of the proposed ViT architecture to that of existing DL techniques.",
    "This will provide a thorough analysis of the benefits and drawbacks of our proposed approach compared to existing methodologies.",
    "• We will evaluate the efficacy of the proposed ViT architecture using a CXR dataset that is publicly available."
  ],
